64
00:04:12,220 --> 00:04:13,220
I'm sorry! I...!

65
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:14,540
No...

66
00:04:15,090 --> 00:04:16,480
I'm just glad you're okay.

67
00:04:18,230 --> 00:04:19,230
By the way,

68
00:04:19,530 --> 00:04:20,530
that kid...

69
00:04:21,140 --> 00:04:22,140
He seems to be lost...

70
00:04:22,577 --> 00:04:25,047
But he starts crying
whenever I try to put him down.

71
00:04:32,380 --> 00:04:33,380
This...

72
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,160
That's so cool.

73
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:39,130
- Mommy bought it for me.
- I see.

74
00:04:39,770 --> 00:04:44,280
- Your mommy is so nice.
- Yeah. Where's my mommy?

75
00:04:44,930 --> 00:04:47,790
I'm sure she'll be here soon.

76
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:49,716
