77
00:04:49,740 --> 00:04:52,259
- looking all over for you.
- Really?

78
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:53,260
Yeah.

79
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:54,740
So, come on.

80
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,360
Here we go...

81
00:05:00,590 --> 00:05:01,800
You're being so brave.

82
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:03,950
Did you cry?

83
00:05:04,110 --> 00:05:05,260
That's amazing...

84
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,660
Yu-kun!

85
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:09,060
Mommy!

86
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,800
I'm so glad you're okay.

87
00:05:16,330 --> 00:05:17,460
Thank goodness...

88
00:05:19,350 --> 00:05:20,626
Don't run off like that again, okay?

89
00:05:20,650 --> 00:05:21,650
Promise me?

90
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:29,380
I'm so sorry about all this...

91
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,600
Um...

92
00:05:30,601 --> 00:05:31,670
I didn't tell you guys...

93
00:05:32,490 --> 00:05:34,659
I told you, you don't have to apologize.

94
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:35,660
But...

95
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:37,870
The fact that you were missing, Hioki,

96
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,840
I didn't tell the teachers either.

97
00:05:40,990 --> 00:05:41,990
It's just that I...

98
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,360
was really worried.

99
00:05:44,330 --> 00:05:45,790
It's not a big deal.

100
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:49,430
Even so, I still caused
trouble for everyone...

101
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,970
It wasn't exactly trouble...

102
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:55,080
I was definitely freaking out, though.

103
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:03,160
But as long as you're okay,

104
00:06:04,470 --> 00:06:05,730
that's all that matters.

105
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,190
Why...

106
00:06:11,910 --> 00:06:12,910
Huh?

107
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,130
Why is Watarai...

108
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:20,810
so kind to me?

109
00:06:23,810 --> 00:06:24,810
Hioki?

110
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,780
I'm too scared to ask.

111
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:31,240
But I want to just come out and ask.

112
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,080
Let's go.

113
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:36,270
Yeah.

114
00:06:40,130 --> 00:06:41,790
Watarai... what do you...

115
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:45,200
like about me?

116
00:06:55,030 --> 00:06:56,430
This time, really...

117
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:58,260
I'm so sorry, everyone.

118
00:06:58,790 --> 00:07:00,560
Hey, don't worry about it!

119
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:02,390
Why are you apologizing anyway?

120
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:05,070
Helping a lost kid is a good thing!

121
00:07:05,650 --> 00:07:06,650
But...

122
00:07:07,090 --> 00:07:08,920
If anything, it was perfect timing.

123
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:12,400
We wanted to take a break anyway.

124
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:14,500
Thank you.

125
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,780
Besides, something fun happened.

126
00:07:17,090 --> 00:07:18,140
Huh? What?

127
00:07:19,420 --> 00:07:20,690
Watarai was totally panicking.

128
00:07:20,691 --> 00:07:21,191
Oh yeah, totally.

129
00:07:21,260 --> 00:07:23,790
- For real!
- He was on a whole other level of worried.

130
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:26,500
- And then he just took off running!
- Yeah.

131
00:07:27,090 --> 00:07:28,390
Well, what was I supposed to do?

132
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:33,160
- I was seriously worried!
- It was super...

133
00:07:37,770 --> 00:07:39,610
- I'm sorry to you girls, too.
- Huh?

134
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,320
Oh, no.

135
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,860
It's fine with us...

136
00:07:43,230 --> 00:07:44,230
Right?

137
00:07:44,590 --> 00:07:47,020
Yeah, don't worry about it at all.

138
00:07:48,290 --> 00:07:49,290
However...

139
00:07:49,730 --> 00:07:51,750
In exchange, you could
do something for us...

140
00:07:52,010 --> 00:07:53,210
There's actually...

141
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:55,520
