- A ghost appeared.

144
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:22,520
I see...

145
00:08:23,130 --> 00:08:25,090
- Whoa!
- No, no, no.

146
00:08:26,910 --> 00:08:28,510
- Whoa!
- That looks so scary!

147
00:08:29,150 --> 00:08:31,719
Well, I can probably guess...

148
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,370
why the girls wanted to come here.

149
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,960
Hey, it's so scary! Guys, come with us!

150
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:38,450
Sure.

151
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,200
But you girls have to lead the way.

152
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:43,950
This guy never changes...

153
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:45,680
But still,

154
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,120
this atmosphere...

155
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:48,680
is actually pretty scary, isn't it?

156
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,160
Hey!

157
00:08:50,330 --> 00:08:52,190
If it gets really scary,
can I hold on to you?

158
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,760
- Absolutely not.
- Hey, you guys...

159
00:08:59,930 --> 00:09:00,930
Hioki.

160
00:09:01,010 --> 00:09:02,010
Aren't you scared?

161
00:09:03,130 --> 00:09:04,770
Huh? Me...?

162
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:11,500
No, I'm not.

163
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,120
If you do get scared,

164
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,370
do you want to hold hands?

165
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:19,040
No... I'm okay.

166
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:23,980
I see.

167
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:42,080
Aah!

168
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:48,000
You've got to be kidding me.

169
00:10:03,220 --> 00:10:04,940
Ah! Wait... Hold on...!
No way...

170
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,040
Everyone...

171
00:10:10,730 --> 00:10:12,380
Man... What is even happening?

172
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,160
If I'd known it was this scary,

173
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:17,990
I should've just... held Watarai's hand.

174
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:25,990
Ah... Is that you, Watarai...?

175
00:10:30,580 --> 00:10:31,580
Watarai...

176
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:36,050
Asking someone to hold my hand...

177
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,730
is just too embarrassing.

178
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:39,910
But you know...

179
00:10:40,330 --> 00:10:41,580
Watarai's hand...

180
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:43,060
is so big.

181
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:46,660
Hioki... Are you okay?

182
00:10:48,820 --> 00:10:51,030
Watarai... is in front of me?

183
00:10:52,270 --> 00:10:53,430
Which means...

184
00:10:53,710 --> 00:10:54,930
this hand is...

185
00:10:59,330 --> 00:11:01,530
Aah!

186
00:11:04,250 --> 00:11:05,450
Please come again.

187
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:07,310
We've been waiting for you.

188
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:15,180
- That was terrifying.
- Holding hands with a mummy...

189
00:11:15,490 --> 00:11:17,290
- That's hilarious!
- Right? By the way...

190
00:11:17,380 --> 00:11:18,910
I never knew Hioki could be so loud.

191
00:11:19,290 --> 00:11:20,930
Tell me about it! His scream...

192
00:11:21,130 --> 00:11:22,730
- was the scariest part.
- I know, right?

193
00:11:23,590 --> 00:11:24,590
Sorry.

194
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:27,970
I should have been next to you.

195
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:30,140
No, it's really okay...

196
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:33,190
I can't believe a mummy
stole you away, Hioki.

197
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,870
What do you mean, 'stole away'?

198
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:38,100
Besides, you guys were all...

199
00:11:38,130 --> 00:11:39,410
scared to death, weren't you?

200
00:11:39,650 --> 00:11:40,850
That's true.

201
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:42,210
Hotta was about to cry.

202
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:43,669
What?! I was not!

203
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:45,970
- Yes, you were!
- Hey... guys... where to next?

204
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:49,000
We only have about 15 minutes left...
Is there anything you want to do last?

205
00:11:50,090 --> 00:11:51,590
We only have 15 minutes left.

206
00:11:51,890 --> 00:11:53,730
Is there anything we
can all ride together now

207
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:55,670
